title: Lies, not gifts
text: My first order was supposed to be free as a reward for installing the app. I spun the reel and won two free items and I had to install the app to get them. I added the products to the cart, installed the app, confirmed the order through the app, paid the full amount and did not receive the promised gifts. I contacted support, they gave me a 20% discount on the next order, but did not compensate the cost of the promised gifts. I can't recommend either the support or the app itself, as I was misled.
